column12: * Apps that cost less than $2.50 on mobile stores are more profitable for us.
* Positive ratings are better and ensure income over time.
* Profitable App Store categories include Reference, Book, Photo & Video, and Productivity.
* Apps are most profitable when listed on both the App Store and the Play Store.

column1: Tsuro - The Game of the Path

column8: A spooky adventure with everyone’s favorite monster!
We all know Halloween is about candy!
...so why not branch out to other sugary sweets?
Some would say it’s the reason for the season!
All Hallow’s Eve isn’t going to remember itself, you know.
